verses.text: \w Praise|strong="H1984"\w* ye \w the|strong="H0853"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*, because psalm \w is|strong="H3068"\w* good: \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w our|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* joyful \w and|strong="H3068"\w* comely \w praise|strong="H1984"\w*.
